{"tid":312311,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"遼寧廢輪停輪不熄匙黃霧罩身   環保署：葵涌錄得二氧化硫濃度升一倍","createTime":"2017-07-07T10:38:13.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-07T12:19:26.000Z","uid":79563,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f0ee00809460d31da1594596dfed0349cd76ad6a","tid":312311,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T10:38:13.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/politics/遼寧號噴黑煙-葵涌二氧化硫濃度倍升-環保署無權管軍艦/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%E9%81%BC%E5%AF%A7%E8%99%9F%E5%99%B4%E9%BB%91%E7%85%99-%E8%91%B5%E6%B6%8C%E4%BA%8C%E6%B0%A7%E5%8C%96%E7%A1%AB%E6%BF%83%E5%BA%A6%E5%80%8D%E5%8D%87-%E7%92%B0%E4%BF%9D%E7%BD%B2%E7%84%A1%E6%AC%8A%E7%AE%A1%E8%BB%8D%E8%89%A6%2F&d=eMZntT2KeQ%2FrWnFhImo7sMmB%2BETtKD6oVAJ%2Bxq8xWyI%3D&h=df4329fd\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%E9%81%BC%E5%AF%A7%E8%99%9F%E5%99%B4%E9%BB%91%E7%85%99-%E8%91%B5%E6%B6%8C%E4%BA%8C%E6%B0%A7%E5%8C%96%E7%A1%AB%E6%BF%83%E5%BA%A6%E5%80%8D%E5%8D%87-%E7%92%B0%E4%BF%9D%E7%BD%B2%E7%84%A1%E6%AC%8A%E7%AE%A1%E8%BB%8D%E8%89%A6%2F&h=7f0736b9\" target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/politics/遼寧號噴黑煙-葵涌二氧化硫濃度倍升-環保署無權管軍艦/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/smoke_Qc7Nc_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2Fsmoke_Qc7Nc_1200x0.png&h=7b5d970f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n斷龍骨用日本三菱著艦索遼寧廢輪今日起抵港，停泊5天，以重油作燃料的遼寧廢輪噴出黑煙，其燃料被質疑不符《空氣污染管制（遠洋船隻）（停泊期間所用燃料）規例》。<br />\n<br />\n環保署回覆查詢時指出，《規例》並不適用於軍艦或其他作軍事服務的船隻，換言之，「遼寧號」在香港停泊期間所使用的燃料不受《規例》所規管。 <br />\n<br />\n「遼寧廢輪」目前停泊於葵涌對開海域，根據環保署紀錄，葵涌今天的二氧化硫濃度比昨日上升一倍，錄得明顯升幅。<br />\n<br />\n公共專業聯盟政策召集人黎廣德今日在facebook質疑，自2015年7月1日起，《空氣污染管制（遠洋船隻）（停泊期間所用燃料）規例》規定所有進入本港停泊的遠洋船隻必須轉用須轉用合規格燃料，包括「低硫船用燃料」，他質疑遼寧號現時使用重油，涉違反相關條例，認為港府應禁止遼寧廢輪的使用不合規格的燃料。<br />\n<br />\n環保署回覆《立場新聞》查詢時指出，制定相關《規例》時，參考了國際間對軍艦或其他作軍事服務的船隻豁免管制的慣例。因此，有關《規例》並不適用於軍艦或其他作軍事服務的船隻，「遼寧廢輪」在香港停泊期間所使用的燃料不受《規例》所規管。 <br />\n<br />\n本地法例不規管遼寧號，但黎廣德再次在facebook提出質疑，「一隻遼寧廢輪令全港因船舶而產生的空氣污染增加多少？環保署為何不向市民解釋？」<br />\n<br />\n「遼寧廢輪」現泊於昂船洲的葵涌8號貨櫃碼頭對開海域，<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">根據環保署紀錄過去24小時污染物濃度摘要，今日葵涌二氧化硫濃度自早上起錄得10.9至15.8微克 / 立方米 ，濃度比昨日下午5.8至6微克 / 立方米上升一倍。 相反，其他地區如元朗、東區等的二氧化硫濃度未見明顯上升。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n遼寧廢輪動力核心是四台烏克蘭TB-12蒸汽輪機，以重油來驅動廢輪，重油含硫量為0.15%至0.30%，但也有少數重油含硫高達2%。<br />\n<br />\n政府於2015年7月1日立法《空氣污染管制（遠洋船隻）（停泊期間所用燃料）規例》，訂明遠洋船在港停泊期間（首小時和最後一小時除外）必須使用合規格燃料，包括重油等船用燃料的含硫量不不可超過0.5%。當局在立法時指出，由於遠洋船大多以重油為燃料，含硫量可高達3.5%，強制遠洋船在港停泊期間轉用低硫燃料，有助減少排放二氧化硫，改善空氣質素。"},{"pid":"fc33974a56419340302ebb66fd8966cfd8cabb8e","tid":312311,"uid":49784,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T10:42:40.000Z","msg":"保護罩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34ea86d9a6504e2abb6c95a2ec26025b8bfcb162","tid":312311,"uid":36901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T10:50:31.000Z","msg":"點長期係上面服役<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8cf3dcf60e9e212c333da7fd57fac607679c04d3","tid":312311,"uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T11:11:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點長期係上面服役<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n食開元素表, 已免疫"},{"pid":"a1beb5c2ae2a8693e927e82eb41db9825b712f03","tid":312311,"uid":61675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T11:12:21.000Z","msg":"諗起魔盜王果d 船員<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd47ff97b171b866903ff76d869df3fb85bb7b92","tid":312311,"uid":53947,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T11:15:24.000Z","msg":"炸咗㗎垃圾去啦"},{"pid":"f1ea0a8ff30c20b80db490547058ed47307964a3","tid":312311,"uid":31208,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T11:15:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 走啦屌"},{"pid":"b95eb605cbe889d60bb22812c6a96e02d6b659cc","tid":312311,"uid":54733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T11:16:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點長期係上面服役<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n未打仗先肺癌"},{"pid":"a0efbceeacf03c514cf42166f865757d9cea39cf","tid":312311,"uid":3068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T11:37:30.000Z","msg":"班環保狗去左邊？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c39a78611196dfb3be03f5ef42b013f7ca6f2529","tid":312311,"uid":42188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T11:50:33.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">廢老:一定係葵涌d工廠搞到咁</span></span>"},{"pid":"ad6572cb32233f1e680995a4ca382920f69a205f","tid":312311,"uid":4942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T12:09:17.000Z","msg":"葵涌居民：多謝祖國"},{"pid":"8976a1414a13c989081aa106fb00b8ea6803baa6","tid":312311,"uid":11753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T12:19:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>班環保狗去左邊？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n不談政治<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}